{"tid":2022569,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：有多名理大手足被捕後被黑警以索帶反綁雙手跪地多個小時","createTime":"2020-05-18T11:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T11:43:56.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3ba8f66e66d6412dd98577501167ee0dc44e404c","tid":2022569,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"去年11月理工大學衝突期間，油尖旺一帶市民「開花」上街營救抗爭者，大批市民被警方拘控，再有十三男兩女被控暴動罪，今午在東區裁判法院提堂。其中有大狀在庭上投訴指被告遭警察毆打，欲要求主任裁判官錢禮記錄在案，惟未及詳述受傷情形，裁判官已叫停，稱留待下次處理。散庭後，多名大律師主動向傳媒披露，多名被告在警署內被當成戰俘對待，以索帶反綁雙手，迫令在停車場跪地多個小時，幾乎「跪天光」，有人因而暈倒，需召救護車送院。<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200518/E4YR6CGHK7VZEKTJYESPRU4FCE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200518%2FE4YR6CGHK7VZEKTJYESPRU4FCE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCpFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=4e1c0588\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200518%2FE4YR6CGHK7VZEKTJYESPRU4FCE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=1d0aa5a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200518/E4YR6CGHK7VZEKTJYESPRU4FCE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"}]}